This project is an arduino project use:
Arduino Nano
Serial MP3 player
FSR - Force Sensing Resistors
Single Addressable LEDS

The code is for fighting a dragon.
The basic is an interaction when you set up 3 FSR one on each hand and one on the head and a small led light near each sensor.
When the light is on you need to hit that area.

When the kid wants to fight the dragon he takes a stick and fight.

For more information please see the article.



